#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:1
msgid "Make Environment"
msgstr "创建环境"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:3
msgid ""
"An IR-SIM simulation is created from a YAML scenario file with "
"`irsim.make()` and driven by a short Python loop (`env.step()` → "
"`env.render()` → `env.done()`). This page covers building the environment, "
"the core loop, status control, and dynamic object management. For running "
"several scenarios at once, see [Multiple environments]"
"(multiple_environments.md)."
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 仿真由 YAML 场景文件通过 `irsim.make()` 创建，并由一段简短的 Python 循"
"环（`env.step()` → `env.render()` → `env.done()`）驱动。本页介绍如何构建环"
"境、核心循环、状态控制以及动态对象管理。若需同时运行多个场景，请参阅[多环境]"
"(multiple_environments.md)。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:5
msgid "Python script and YAML configuration file"
msgstr "Python 脚本与 YAML 配置文件"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:7
msgid ""
"To start the simulation, you need to create an environment. The environment "
"is a container for all the objects in the simulation. It is also responsible "
"for updating the state of the simulation at each time step."
msgstr ""
"要开始仿真，需要先创建一个环境。环境是仿真中所有对象的容器，并负责在每个时间"
"步更新仿真状态。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:0
msgid "Python Script"
msgstr "Python 脚本"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:13
msgid "Create your environment with a simple Python script:"
msgstr "可以使用简单的 Python 脚本创建环境："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:20
msgid ""
"The `make` function creates an environment from a configuration file. "
"Supported parameters include:"
msgstr "`make` 函数会根据配置文件创建环境，支持的参数包括："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:22
msgid ""
"**`world_name`** (str, optional): Path to the world YAML configuration file"
msgstr "**`world_name`**（str，可选）：世界 YAML 配置文件路径"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:23
msgid ""
"**`projection`** (str, optional): Projection type (\"3d\" for 3D "
"environment, None for 2D)"
msgstr ""
"**`projection`**（str，可选）：投影类型（“3d” 表示 3D 环境，None 表示 2D）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:24
msgid ""
"**`display`** (bool): Whether to display the environment visualization "
"(default: True)"
msgstr "**`display`**（bool）：是否显示环境可视化（默认 True）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:25
msgid ""
"**`save_ani`** (bool): Whether to save the simulation as an animation "
"(default: False)"
msgstr "**`save_ani`**（bool）：是否将仿真保存为动图（默认 False）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:26
msgid ""
"**`log_level`** (str): Logging level for the environment (default: \"INFO\")"
msgstr "**`log_level`**（str）：环境日志级别（默认 \"INFO\"）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:27
msgid ""
"**`seed`** (int, optional): Seed for IR-SIM's project RNG. If provided, "
"random elements produced by IR-SIM become reproducible. If omitted/``None``, "
"a new unseeded generator is used (non-reproducible). Custom extensions using "
"``np.random`` or Python ``random`` should either switch to IR-SIM's RNG or "
"be seeded separately."
msgstr ""
"**`seed`**（int，可选）：IR-SIM 随机数引擎的种子。提供后，IR-SIM 生成的随机内"
"容即可复现；若省略或为 ``None``，则使用未设种子的生成器（不可复现）。若自定义"
"扩展仍使用 ``np.random`` 或 Python ``random``，需改用 IR-SIM RNG 或另行设定种"
"子。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:33
msgid ""
"For more details, see the {py:class}`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase` class "
"documentation."
msgstr "更多信息见 {py:class}`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase` 类文档。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:0
msgid "YAML Configuration"
msgstr "YAML 配置"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:38
msgid "Define a minimal running world in a YAML file (`basic_world.yaml`):"
msgstr "在 YAML 文件（`basic_world.yaml`）中定义一个最小可运行世界："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:63
msgid ""
"The configuration file defines the world and the robot that the main loop "
"advances from its start to its goal."
msgstr "配置文件定义世界和机器人，主循环将机器人从起点推进到目标。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:0
msgid "Demonstration"
msgstr "演示"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:68
msgid "A single robot running the IR-SIM step, render, and done loop"
msgstr "单个机器人运行 IR-SIM 的 step、render 和 done 循环"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:75
msgid "Important Parameters Explanation"
msgstr "重要参数说明"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:77
msgid "World Configuration"
msgstr "世界配置"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:79
msgid ""
"**`world`**: Main section that defines the simulation environment properties"
msgstr "**`world`**：定义仿真环境属性的主段"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:80
msgid ""
"**`height`** and **`width`**: Specify the size of the simulation world in "
"meters"
msgstr "**`height`** 与 **`width`**：以米为单位指定世界尺寸"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:81
msgid ""
"**`step_time`**: Controls simulation accuracy and speed (smaller = more "
"accurate, slower)"
msgstr "**`step_time`**：控制仿真精度与速度（越小越精确但更慢）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:82
msgid ""
"**`sample_time`**: Controls rendering frequency (larger = faster simulation, "
"less smooth visualization)"
msgstr "**`sample_time`**：控制渲染频率（越大仿真越快，可视化越不平滑）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:83
msgid ""
"**`offset`**: Shifts the world coordinate system origin [x, y] in meters"
msgstr "**`offset`**：以米为单位偏移世界坐标系原点 [x, y]"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:84
msgid "**`control_mode`**: Determines how the simulation is controlled"
msgstr "**`control_mode`**：决定仿真控制方式"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:85
msgid "`'auto'`: Automatic simulation execution"
msgstr "`'auto'`：自动执行仿真"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:86
msgid "`'keyboard'`: Manual keyboard control"
msgstr "`'keyboard'`：手动键盘控制"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:87
msgid "**`collision_mode`**: Defines collision detection behavior"
msgstr "**`collision_mode`**：定义碰撞检测行为"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:88
msgid "`'stop'`: Stop simulation when collision occurs (default)"
msgstr "`'stop'`：发生碰撞时停止仿真（默认）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:89
msgid "`'unobstructed'`: Ignore all collisions"
msgstr "`'unobstructed'`：忽略所有碰撞"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:90
msgid "`'unobstructed_obstacles'`: Ignore only obstacle collisions"
msgstr "`'unobstructed_obstacles'`：仅忽略障碍物碰撞"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:91
msgid ""
"**`obstacle_map`**: Optional. Path to an obstacle map image, or a generator "
"spec (e.g. `{ name: perlin, ... }`). See [Configure grid map]"
"(configure_grid_map)."
msgstr ""
"**`obstacle_map`**：可选。障碍物地图图像的路径，或生成器配置（例如 `{ name: "
"perlin, ... }`）。参见 [配置栅格地图](configure_grid_map)。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:93
msgid "Performance Considerations"
msgstr "性能考量"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:95
msgid "**Smaller `step_time`**: More accurate physics but slower simulation"
msgstr "**更小的 `step_time`**：物理更精确但仿真更慢"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:96
msgid ""
"**Larger `sample_time`**: Faster simulation but less smooth visualization"
msgstr "**更大的 `sample_time`**：仿真更快但可视化不够流畅"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:97
msgid "**World size**: Larger worlds require more computational resources"
msgstr "**世界尺寸**：更大的世界需要更多算力"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:100
msgid ""
"You can use `sample_time` to control the rendering frequency and accelerate "
"the simulation speed. The default value of `sample_time` is the same as "
"`step_time`."
msgstr ""
"可以通过 `sample_time` 控制渲染频率、提升仿真速度。默认情况下 `sample_time` "
"与 `step_time` 相同。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:103
msgid ""
"For more detailed parameter information, see the [YAML Configuration](../"
"yaml_config/configuration.md) reference."
msgstr "更详细的参数说明参见 [YAML 配置](../yaml_config/configuration.md)。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:106
msgid ""
"**Automatic Configuration Detection**: The default YAML configuration file "
"has the same name as your Python script. For example, if you create a script "
"named `test.py`, IR-SIM automatically looks for `test.yaml` in the same "
"directory."
msgstr ""
"**自动配置检测**：默认 YAML 配置文件与 Python 脚本同名。例如脚本为 "
"`test.py`，IR-SIM 会在同目录自动寻找 `test.yaml`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:115
msgid ""
"This feature simplifies development by eliminating the need to specify "
"configuration files explicitly."
msgstr "该特性避免手动指定配置文件，简化了开发流程。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:118
msgid "Basic Simulation Loop"
msgstr "基础仿真循环"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:120
msgid "After creating an environment, you'll typically run a simulation loop:"
msgstr "创建环境后，通常会运行如下仿真循环："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:138
msgid "Core Methods Explained"
msgstr "核心方法说明"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:140
msgid "**`env.step()`**: Advances the simulation by one time step"
msgstr "**`env.step()`**：让仿真前进一步"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:141
msgid ""
"**`env.render(interval)`**: Updates the visualization with specified time "
"interval between frames"
msgstr "**`env.render(interval)`**：按设定的帧间隔刷新可视化"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:142
msgid ""
"**`env.done()`**: Returns `True` if simulation completion conditions are met"
msgstr "**`env.done()`**：当满足结束条件时返回 `True`"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:143
msgid ""
"**`env.reset(random=False)`**: Restores objects to their initial states. "
"With `random=True`, rebuilds the world from the cached YAML parse so any "
"randomized elements (e.g. `distribution: random`, random shape generators) "
"are re-sampled from the current RNG state. Use it together with "
"`irsim.util.random.set_seed(seed)` for reproducible fresh scenes. The YAML "
"file on disk is **not** re-read; to pick up on-disk edits, use "
"`env.reload()` instead."
msgstr ""
"**`env.reset(random=False)`**：将对象恢复为初始状态。传入 `random=True` 时，"
"会基于缓存的 YAML 解析结果重建世界，从而让随机元素（如 `distribution: "
"random`、随机形状生成器）按当前 RNG 状态重新采样 —— 可配合 "
"`irsim.util.random.set_seed(seed)` 获得可复现的全新场景。此操作**不会**重新读"
"取磁盘上的 YAML 文件；如需加载磁盘上的修改，请改用 `env.reload()`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:144
msgid ""
"**`env.refresh()`**: Refreshes state-derived attributes (geometry, sensor "
"readings, collision tree, and status) without advancing the simulation. "
"Useful after mutating object states directly (e.g. `robot.set_state(...)`) "
"when you need sensors and collisions brought up to date before the next "
"`env.step()`."
msgstr ""
"**`env.refresh()`**：在不推进仿真的前提下，刷新由状态派生的属性（几何、传感器"
"读数、碰撞树以及状态）。当你直接修改对象状态（例如 `robot.set_state(...)`）"
"后，若希望在下一次 `env.step()` 之前让传感器和碰撞信息同步到最新状态，使用此"
"方法。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:145
msgid ""
"**`env.reload(world_name=None)`**: Re-parses the YAML file (optionally a "
"different one) and rebuilds world/objects."
msgstr ""
"**`env.reload(world_name=None)`**：重新解析 YAML 文件（可选指定其他文件）并重"
"建世界/对象。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:146
msgid "**`env.end()`**: Properly closes the environment and releases resources"
msgstr "**`env.end()`**：正确关闭环境并释放资源"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:147
msgid ""
"**`env.close()`**: Alias for `env.end()`, provided for [Gym](https://"
"gymnasium.farama.org/)-style API compatibility"
msgstr ""
"**`env.close()`**：`env.end()` 的别名，提供 [Gym](https://"
"gymnasium.farama.org/) 风格的 API 兼容性"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:150
msgid "Update order"
msgstr "更新顺序"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:152
msgid ""
"The environment advances all objects first, then updates all sensors. This "
"two-phase update ensures sensors read the latest world state consistently. "
"If you step objects manually, either pass `sensor_step=True` to "
"`ObjectBase.step(...)` or call `obj.sensor_step()` after updating states."
msgstr ""
"环境会先推进所有对象，再更新全部传感器。这种两阶段更新保证传感器读取到的都是"
"最新世界状态。若手动推进对象，请在 `ObjectBase.step(...)` 传入 "
"`sensor_step=True`，或在更新对象状态后调用 `obj.sensor_step()`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:155
msgid "Environment Control and Status"
msgstr "环境控制与状态"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:157
msgid "Status Management"
msgstr "状态管理"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:191
msgid "Runtime Status Values"
msgstr "运行时状态值"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:193
msgid ""
"IR-SIM updates `env.status` as the simulation runs. The YAML `world.status` "
"setting only supplies the initial display label; it does not pause, resume, "
"or stop execution."
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 会在仿真运行时更新 `env.status`。YAML 中的 `world.status` 设置仅提供初"
"始显示标签；它不会暂停、恢复或停止执行。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:195
msgid "**`\"Running\"`**: The environment is running in auto control mode"
msgstr "**`\"Running\"`**：环境在自动控制模式运行"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:196
msgid ""
"**`\"Running (keyboard)\"`**: The environment is running in keyboard control "
"mode"
msgstr "**`\"Running (keyboard)\"`**：环境在键盘控制模式运行"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:197
msgid "**`\"Pause\"`**: Simulation is paused"
msgstr "**`\"Pause\"`**：仿真已暂停"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:198
msgid "**`\"Arrived\"`**: All robots have arrived at their goals"
msgstr "**`\"Arrived\"`**：所有机器人都到达目标"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:199
msgid "**`\"Collision\"`**: A collision has occurred"
msgstr "**`\"Collision\"`**：检测到碰撞"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:200
msgid "**`\"Pause (Debugging)\"`**: Debugging mode (when `F5` key is pressed)"
msgstr "**`\"Pause (Debugging)\"`**：调试模式（按下 `F5` 时）"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:201
msgid "**`\"Reset\"`**: The environment is reset"
msgstr "**`\"Reset\"`**：环境已复位"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:202
msgid "**`\"Reload\"`**: The environment is reloaded"
msgstr "**`\"Reload\"`**：环境已重新加载"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:203
msgid "**`\"Save Figure\"`**: The figure is saved"
msgstr "**`\"Save Figure\"`**：已保存图像"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:204
msgid "**`\"Quit\"`**: The environment is quit"
msgstr "**`\"Quit\"`**：环境已退出"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:207
msgid "Configure Environment Title"
msgstr "配置环境标题"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:209
msgid ""
"By default, the simulation time and status are shown in the environment "
"title. You can customize this behavior by setting the `show_title` and "
"customizing the title by `env.set_title()`."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，环境标题会显示仿真时间与状态。可通过设置 `show_title` 并调用 "
"`env.set_title()` 来自定义该行为。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:0
msgid "Custom Title Configuration"
msgstr "自定义标题配置"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:0
msgid "Enable/Disable Title Display"
msgstr "启用/禁用标题显示"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:251
msgid "Dynamic Object Management"
msgstr "动态对象管理"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:253
msgid ""
"In addition to defining objects in YAML configuration files, you can create "
"and add objects programmatically at runtime. This is useful for spawning "
"objects dynamically during simulation, such as generating random obstacles "
"or adding robots on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"除了在 YAML 配置文件中定义对象外，还可以在运行时通过代码动态创建和添加对象。"
"这适用于在仿真过程中动态生成对象，例如随机生成障碍物或动态添加机器人。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:255
msgid "Creating Objects Programmatically"
msgstr "通过代码创建对象"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:257
msgid ""
"Use `env.create_robot()` and `env.create_obstacle()` to create objects with "
"keyword arguments:"
msgstr ""
"使用 `env.create_robot()` 和 `env.create_obstacle()` 通过关键字参数创建对象："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:281
msgid "Common keyword arguments include:"
msgstr "常用关键字参数包括："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:283
msgid ""
"**`kinematics`** (dict): Kinematics model, e.g. `{\"name\": \"diff\"}`, "
"`{\"name\": \"omni\"}`, `{\"name\": \"acker\"}`. Omit or use `{\"name\": "
"\"static\"}` for static objects."
msgstr ""
"**`kinematics`**（dict）：运动学模型，如 `{\"name\": \"diff\"}`、`{\"name\": "
"\"omni\"}`、`{\"name\": \"acker\"}`。省略或使用 `{\"name\": \"static\"}` 表示"
"静态对象。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:284
msgid ""
"**`shape`** (dict): Shape definition, e.g. `{\"name\": \"circle\", "
"\"radius\": 0.5}` or `{\"name\": \"polygon\", \"vertices\": [[0,0],[1,0],"
"[0,1]]}`."
msgstr ""
"**`shape`**（dict）：形状定义，如 `{\"name\": \"circle\", \"radius\": 0.5}` "
"或 `{\"name\": \"polygon\", \"vertices\": [[0,0],[1,0],[0,1]]}`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:285
msgid "**`state`** (list): Initial state `[x, y, theta, ...]`."
msgstr "**`state`**（list）：初始状态 `[x, y, theta, ...]`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:286
msgid "**`goal`** (list): Goal state `[x, y, theta, ...]`."
msgstr "**`goal`**（list）：目标状态 `[x, y, theta, ...]`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:287
msgid "**`color`** (str): Object color (default varies by kinematics type)."
msgstr "**`color`**（str）：对象颜色（默认值因运动学类型而异）。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:288
msgid ""
"**`name`** (str): Unique object name. Must not conflict with existing "
"objects."
msgstr "**`name`**（str）：唯一对象名称，不能与已有对象重名。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:289
msgid ""
"**`goal_threshold`** (float): Distance threshold for arrival detection "
"(default: 0.1)."
msgstr "**`goal_threshold`**（float）：到达检测的距离阈值（默认 0.1）。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:291
msgid ""
"For the full list of parameters, see the {py:class}"
"`~irsim.world.object_base.ObjectBase` class documentation."
msgstr ""
"完整参数列表参见 {py:class}`~irsim.world.object_base.ObjectBase` 类文档。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:293
msgid "Adding Objects to the Environment"
msgstr "向环境添加对象"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:295
msgid ""
"After creating objects, add them to the environment with `env.add_object()` "
"or `env.add_objects()`:"
msgstr ""
"创建对象后，使用 `env.add_object()` 或 `env.add_objects()` 将其添加到环境中："

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:305
msgid ""
"Each object must have a unique name. Adding an object with a duplicate name "
"raises a `ValueError`."
msgstr "每个对象必须有唯一名称。添加重名对象会引发 `ValueError`。"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:307
msgid "See also"
msgstr "另请参阅"

#: ../../source/usage/make_environment.md:309
msgid ""
"[Multiple environments](multiple_environments.md): run several scenarios at "
"once with isolated state, for comparison studies or reinforcement-learning "
"training."
msgstr ""
"[多环境](multiple_environments.md) —— 以相互隔离的状态同时运行多个场景，适用"
"于对比研究或强化学习训练。"
